title: Episode 59: Ft Lee Mazin
itunes:title: Episode 59: Ft Lee Mazin
description:
Fresh off the premiere of season 3 of Sisterhood of Hip-hop, Lee Mazin pops by Lip Service to chat with hosts Angela Yee, Stephanie Santiago, and Gigi Maguire about whether or not you can be in love with 2 people at the same time, asking someone you are dating for career help, and whether or not you should tell your boyfriend everything (like who's in your dm's).
